{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><h1 id=\"A6WD6\"><span class=\"ne-text\">插入附件</span></h1><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"uf0e973b0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">加号插入：通过左上角的卡片插入菜单，可以选择「附件」卡片。</span></li></ol><p id=\"u03ef9e19\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1662528942358-d64f3c9e-aee8-45d5-96e2-1de03dcb31a0.png\" width=\"214\" id=\"LzmkE\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ud9e21c30\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ol start=\"2\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"udbcafde4\"><span class=\"ne-text\">直接拖入文件：在本地文件夹中直接拖入文件到编辑态的语雀文档中，即可完成附件插入。</span></li><li id=\"u9d09157f\"><span class=\"ne-text\">快捷键添加：输入</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/fj</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/附件</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/fujian</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/attachment</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> ，即可唤起本地文件选择弹窗。</span></li></ol><h1 id=\"tHT1V\"><span class=\"ne-text\">选择形态</span></h1><p id=\"298670aa7fba45af29112f6569f076e0_p_12\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">插入附件后，根据可解析的形态，会弹出形态选择弹窗。可选择标题格式、卡片格式、嵌入格式等。</span></p><p id=\"u61fe8f14\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1662529527713-03c43016-87b9-414e-83f9-c5f742179879.png\" width=\"239\" id=\"ube2881f9\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uda539b65\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"2369fafe89fae403079018df6f36b51b_p_13\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h1 id=\"gdC9p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">预览</span></h1><p id=\"7cf79ceeaaf91ef14264b4c55c1c8c1d_p_14\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"5f032e52af5c497f9855989b70b079ad_p_15\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">附件卡片还有一个特色功能，就是允许直接在线预览附件内容，无须下载。</span></p><p id=\"97c047a084e4bf32f2aa42faf2b6e2fe_p_17\" class=\"ne-p\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/attachments/yuque/0/2020/docx/289938/1601380178073-f1f2f184-bbf4-4c2f-a135-1e5befc08510.docx\" id=\"t8KWf\" class=\"ne-card-file\">📎产品_接入文档模板-1.7.docx</a></p><p id=\"u4aaf4079\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1662529758941-3e89d33a-86be-4ad0-a3b2-4924235d2ac2.png\" width=\"362\" id=\"ue2bbd758\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"c4c8cf8a26b55060e684fc9733b06494_p_19\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"db841a6e995b001085603629a3ace379_p_20\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"0c8077df95c9d9a7b7fd355d7b2f4e35_p_21\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">支持在线预览的文件格式如下：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"87a050c21e68b8f0aa4ef5af5d766eeb_li_0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">PDF</span></li><li id=\"adffb0c6a9878d5df44baab51cdf7153_li_1\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Office 文件：Word, Excel, PPT</span></li><li id=\"05349dd67b364b7cfafad9c921f323cb_li_2\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Mac 办公文件：Keynote, Numbers, Pages</span></li><li id=\"7df9b28dd3a54ce169ed9731b364bbd0_li_3\"><span class=\"ne-text\">脑图：XMind,</span></li><li id=\"c6e36461701087a70d762b43947dec4c_li_4\"><span class=\"ne-text\">原型设计稿：axure 文件（ </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">.rp</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 后缀）</span></li></ul><p id=\"u000dfd9a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u7604f703\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h1 id=\"wVCla\"><span class=\"ne-text\">阅读端下载选项</span></h1><p id=\"29c882451898347f4e240ff1f456d86e_p_24\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果你只想让阅读者只能在线预览，而不想让他们下载附件，可以设置「阅读可下载」的勾选弹窗。</span></p><p id=\"u6dd43b15\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/268442/1662529545132-1b8b309e-6afc-4bf2-a76d-5ebd253dd11e.png\" width=\"329\" id=\"u16e0d3b9\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u7ad29e73\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"ue4f486db\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">更多嵌入形态格式介绍，详见「</span><a href=\"./uilmir\" data-href=\"./uilmir\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">嵌入本地文件</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">」</span></p><p id=\"u7de352b3\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h1 id=\"aywtr\"><span class=\"ne-text\">支持插入的格式</span></h1><p id=\"ue32c5e69\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u12d48569\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">详见</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/ca13hg\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/yuque/gpvawt/ca13hg\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">《支持插入的附件格式》</span></a></p><p id=\"d8f02fc6e1d9d5e68b5ff128662a6b29_p_29\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ue04c8f9a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u425aaf81\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"58edab18de1c8434bf226aab907be2e9_p_30\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道 </span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">， 感谢你的支持！</span></p></div>",
  "slug": 13900840,
  "title": "如何插入附件"
}